data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 4 Bedrooms 2.5 Bathrooms Colonial, Located on a 3.36 Acres.  The Main level has a  Large Living Room and Dining Room  with crown molding and a large Table space Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances and new  backsplash. Continue on to a Huge Family room with a walkout to the backyard. The home also boasts a lovely front porch where you can enjoy a nice  sunrise and sunset. The upstairs level has 3 roomy bedrooms and a Hall Bath, A spacious Primary Bedroom with its own Bathroom with Shower. New backyard doors and front door.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this lovely property your own! Schedule your appointment today to view this amazing home!
